text: Hogebrug is a village in the Dutch province of South Holland. It is a part of the former municipality of Reeuwijk, and lies about 6 km east of Gouda. The statistical area "Hogebrug", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 120.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005.
